### Create question
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Who is Barcelona's all time leading scorer?",
  "difficulty": "EASY",
  "explanation": "Lionel Messi is Barcelona's all time leading scorer with 700 goals.",
  "categoryId": 2,
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "text": "Samuel Eto'o",
      "correct": false
    },
    {
      "text": "Luis Suarez",
      "correct": false
    },
    {
      "text": "Lionel Messi",
      "correct": true
    },
    {
      "text": "Neymar",
      "correct": false
    }
  ]
}

### Get all questions
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions

### Get question by id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions/1

### Get questions by category
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions/category/2

### Create invalid question - two correct answers
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Invalid test question?",
  "difficulty": "EASY",
  "explanation": "Testing validation.",
  "categoryId": 2,
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "text": "Option A",
      "correct": true
    },
    {
      "text": "Option B",
      "correct": true
    }
  ]
}